# Project Context

This is a static website portfolio hosted on Vercel.

## Project Type
- **Static Site**: No build process required
- **Hosting**: Vercel (static file serving)
- **Framework**: None - pure HTML/CSS/JavaScript

## Project Structure
- `index.html` - Main portfolio homepage (served at `/`)
- `scripts/dashboard.html` - Interactive dashboard (served at `/scripts/dashboard.html`)
- `vercel.json` - Vercel deployment configuration

## Key Technologies
- **Visualization**: Chart.js, Leaflet.js (loaded via CDN)
- **Styling**: Inline CSS in HTML files
- **Data**: Hardcoded in JavaScript (no external data files needed for deployment)

## Deployment Notes
- All dependencies are loaded from CDNs (no npm packages needed for runtime)
- Large data files are gitignored and not deployed
- Dashboard data is embedded directly in the HTML/JS
- Vercel auto-detects static sites and serves files from root directory

## Development
- No build step required
- Edit HTML files directly
- Test locally by opening HTML files in browser or using a simple HTTP server

